column5: The Faculty of Science and Mathematics or Building Y or Building Ijo is one of the faculties of Satya Wacana Christian University. This faculty has five departments, namely Bachelor of Chemistry, Mathematics, Physics, Physics Education and Master of Data Science. This faculty is located close to a cupola parking lot, shady cafe and library. For this review, I am reviewing for a chemical facility. For their own facilities, they have adequate equipment such as HPLC, spectrophotometer, protein distillator and so on to carry out research and testing. The lecturers who teach the chemistry department are also good and very experienced in various fields such as organic, inorganic and analytical.
